WEBVTT

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:32.376
psixopatlarning amigdalasi 18-20 foiz

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.000
o’rtacha amigdaladan kichikroq.

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:38.736
Bu topilmalarning bari ishonchli

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:40.216
va ular juda qiziqarli.

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:41.896
Asosiy maqsadim kishilar nega

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:45.456
boshqalar haqida qayg’urmasligini 
emas buning aksi

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:47.040
qayg'urishini tushunish edi

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:50.176
Muhim savol esa shunday,

00:05:50.200 --> 00:05:52.456
psixopatiyadan tubdan farq qiluvchi,

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.696
odamiylik va birovlarga yordam qo’lini

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:58.136
cho’zishni ko’zlovchi altruizm

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:02.176
psixopatiyadan o'zgacha miya ta’sirida 
yuz berishi mumkinmi?